#varlist="cct ci clivi clt clwvi hfls hfss hurs huss prc pr prsn prw ps rldscs rlds rlus rlutcs rlut rsdscs rsds rsuscs rsus rsut sci sfcWind tasmax tasmin tas tauu tauv ts uas vas"
